    {
      "name": "6️⃣ PAYMENT SERVICE - RAZORPAY INTEGRATION",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "6.1 Initiate Payment",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.environment.set('RAZORPAY_ORDER_ID', jsonData.razorpayOrderId);",
                  "    pm.environment.set('PAYMENT_ID', jsonData.id);",
                  "    console.log('✅ Razorpay Order ID: ' + jsonData.razorpayOrderId);",
                  "    console.log('✅ Payment ID: ' + jsonData.id);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{CUSTOMER_TOKEN}}"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"policyId\": {{POLICY_ID}},\n  \"amount\": 5000,\n  \"description\": \"Premium payment for Health Plus policy\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{PAYMENT_BASE_URL}}/api/payments/initiate",
              "host": [
                "{{PAYMENT_BASE_URL}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "payments",
                "initiate"
              ]
            },
            "description": "💳 Initiate Razorpay payment\n\n**✅ TOKEN:** {{CUSTOMER_TOKEN}}\n\n**SAVES:**\n- {{RAZORPAY_ORDER_ID}} - For Razorpay checkout\n- {{PAYMENT_ID}} - Payment reference\n\n**RESPONSE:**\n```json\n{\n  \"id\": 1,\n  \"razorpayOrderId\": \"order_xyz123\",\n  \"razorpayKeyId\": \"rzp_live_abc123\",\n  \"amount\": 5000,\n  \"status\": \"INITIATED\"\n}\n```\n\n**NEXT STEPS:**\n1. Use razorpayOrderId in your frontend Razorpay checkout\n2. After payment success, call 6.2 (Confirm Payment)\n3. After payment failure, call 6.3 (Fail Payment)"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "6.2 Confirm Payment (After Razorpay Success)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{CUSTOMER_TOKEN}}"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"razorpayOrderId\": \"{{RAZORPAY_ORDER_ID}}\",\n  \"razorpayPaymentId\": \"pay_Jda834jd2334\",\n  \"razorpaySignature\": \"9ef4dffbfd84f1318f6739a3ce19f9d85851857ae648f114332d8401e0949a3d\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{PAYMENT_BASE_URL}}/api/payments/confirm",
              "host": [
                "{{PAYMENT_BASE_URL}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "payments",
                "confirm"
              ]
            },
            "description": "✅ Confirm payment after successful Razorpay transaction\n\n**✅ TOKEN:** {{CUSTOMER_TOKEN}}\n\n**REQUIRED:** \n- razorpayPaymentId (from Razorpay response)\n- razorpaySignature (from Razorpay success callback)\n\n**RESPONSE:**\n```json\n{\n  \"id\": 1,\n  \"status\": \"SUCCESS\",\n  \"amount\": 5000,\n  \"paidAt\": \"2026-03-30T12:00:00\"\n}\n```"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "6.3 Fail Payment (If User Dismisses)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
